'''Wintrium''' was a liquid that spouted from the [[Fountain of Ancients]] in the [[Derelkoos Desert]] on [[Klatooine/Legends|Klatooine]]. As it reached the surface, it reacted with the dry desert air to create a [[Glass/Legends|glass]]-like material, appearing to be frozen in [[Time/Legends|time]]. Wintrium became harder as it aged, and given enough time it could become nearly indestructible. During the ''[[Starstalker]]''{{'s}} [[Violation|mission]] to retrieve wintrium from the Fountain, the [[Sith Saber]]s [[Anyul]] and [[Marjaak]] used their [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsabers]] to cut wintrium from the sculpture, although even with their lightsabers it was nearly impossible to cut. The [[Fruit/Legends|fruit]] [[pak'pah]] could be grown only on Klatooine, and many [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]] attributed this to the presence of wintrium in the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] soil.

